{"tid":2128033,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人因為呢一年嘅事脾氣差咗好撚多","createTime":"2020-07-27T16:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T14:48:58.000Z","uid":325757,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8eb0f38110129c78ae2df45158a8f687832df119","tid":2128033,"uid":325757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:16:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前真係好好脾氣 俾人話開份人nice 識照顧人而且好多細節位會留意到<br />\n<br />\n但係呢一年發生嘅嘢好似搞到我脾氣變到好差 無耐性，唔想同蠢人解釋太多，尤其涉及一啲嘢需要認真嘅時候，只係想同佢講一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母臭閪問你老尾咩 照做就係啦仆街 <br />\n一係街同人爭執尤其是佢過佢係廢中廢老或者死mk的話係完全唔想再口舌之爭落去，如果一來回有兩三句係feel到條友蠢閪嚟嘅話就唔會再想講落去，會想直接開佢波打佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然到最後都係無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身一年前係唔會有呢啲諗法 而且對住大部份人都係友善有禮貌，最多係怕醜內向啲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家直頭eq又差，而且又會唔想睬一啲講極唔明嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對住正常人係無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一樣咁nice，對住傻閪嘅話啲陋習又出曬嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80475606bfc191ef90e7247e6ddc7df2e53e87fd","tid":2128033,"uid":337986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:21:45.000Z","msg":"睇到你篇嘢我以為係我自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7132bdfda04a4d461317b72c509981c38abfaf82","tid":2128033,"uid":240150,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:25:26.000Z","msg